		<!-- Indentation -->
		<key>increaseIndentPattern</key>
		<string>(?x)
			^ \s* \b(entity|architecture|case)\b .* is \s* $
			| ^ \s* ([a-zA-z][a-zA-z0-9_]*)? \s* : \s* (?i:process)
			| ^ \s* \b(generic|port) (\s* map)? \s* \( \s* $
			| ^ \s* \bbegin\b \s* $
			| ^ \s* if.*then \s* $
